subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: When did Rajasthan become independent from Mughal Empire?
question_hi: अर्थां क्या राज्य 1947 में अमेरूस मुग्ल जमीन के निवर्तीना है।
explanation_en: Rajasthan gained independence from the Mughal Empire in 1947.
